    <arm_group_type>Experimental</arm_group_type>
    <description>An automatic electronic stop of the tmp/sulfa or warfarin order whenever a resident or nurse practitioner places an order for tmp/sulfa with an already active warfarin order, or when ordering both simultaneously</description>
